# The great salad

## Topping

1 Tomato
4 Garlic cloves
40g Red Onion
1C nuts (half cashew, hald pinenuts)
1/3C Deactivated yeast
1/3C Olive oil
Salt
1/2tbsb herb mare

## Salad

3 lettuces
2 grated carrots
1 Diced tomato

## Instructions

Blend the topping. Chop up the lettuces, add topping, then add tomatoes and grated carot.



